{"parse":{"title":"Darkshore Grouper","pageid":121807,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||2}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_26\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=12238\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|ilvl=15\n|name=Darkshore Grouper\n|level=5\n|effect=Use: Restores 243 health over 21 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n__NOTOC__\n==Source==\nThis item can be fished in the sea waters of [[Darkshore]]. While it is the objective of a quest, it is not a quest item per se, and can be caught while not on the quest. \n\n==Darkshore Grouper as a quest objective==\nThis item is an objective of {{questlong|alliance|14|The Family and the Fishing Pole|id=1141}}, which rewards the [[fishing|fisherman]] with the {{loot|common|Blump Family Fishing Pole}}.\n\nIt is worthwhile to pick up the {{questlong|alliance|12|Gaffer Jacks|id=1579}} fishing quest from {{NPC||Wizbang Cranktoggle}} on the second floor in the Inn and do them concurrently. Both require random catches from the same water. \n\n==Notes==\nThere is no cooking recipe for this fish. It can be eaten raw.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|12238}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/darkshore_grouper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common quest items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}